            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Plant size, flowering synchrony and edge effects: What, how and where they affect the reproductive success of a Neotropical tree species: Reproductive Success in <i>Senefeldera Verticillata</i>",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Jakeline Prata De Assis",
                    "lastName": "Pires"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ary Gomes Da",
