            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "The Gulf Coast Health Alliance: Health Risks Related to the Macondo Spill (GC-HARMS) Study: Self-Reported Health Effects",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Sharon",
